{"tid":1179124,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"朱古力囊腫真係會不孕嗎？","createTime":"2019-05-31T01:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T02:52:48.000Z","uid":210705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ac7bed5c12749227f5410fbde719e9cbfebd80","tid":1179124,"uid":210705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"請問有冇絲打驗過有朱古力囊腫?<br />\n上年7月婚前檢查嘅時候驗到有<br />\n睇過3個醫生，有2個就叫盡快手術，有1個就叫試下造人先<br />\n當時因為準備今年3月結婚，所以未有手術又未有試造人<br />\n結婚後試左個幾月都唔成功<br />\n想考慮手術，但手術又話會有機會影響卵巢功能<br />\n同埋手術後都有機會復發<br />\n有冇絲打有相關經驗可以分享下<br />\n心急人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93bdf414aa927306152f24b4f84608b3706a632","tid":1179124,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:46:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會遲咗啲 btw祝你冇事啦"},{"pid":"4a72880628a0148c45824c297720615485bbeeff","tid":1179124,"uid":185217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"應該depends你個瘤喺子宮/輪卵管嘅咩位置 大小 嚴重程度 壓住幾多嘢喎<br />\n咁少info好難答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8e9a77702e8a0ef2d46a930c5ad0e3c3e4c35d","tid":1179124,"uid":185217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff12d92a2de19fc0d05d60763396cf1cb845c06d","tid":1179124,"uid":22141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:40:44.000Z","msg":"要睇吓你個囊腫有幾大<br />\n係會大大減低懷孕機率<br />\n<br />\n而家你一係盡快懷孕一係就做手術之後再計劃懷孕<br />\n因為懷孕-&gt;停經一年-&gt;俾子宮休息<br />\n其實做手術切完唔代表件事完左<br />\n因為你會繼續經期 然後又經血倒流 然後又生過囊腫"},{"pid":"7bad6660917510d398a6e6aceaaf8f0c2526e147","tid":1179124,"uid":22141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4f67e273db9d5418635101cb73164b74904000","tid":1179124,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:52:48.000Z","msg":"你係唔係都一定要做手術架喇<br />\nBB 隨緣喇<br />\n問醫生喇"}]}